1
00:00:11,958 --> 00:00:13,333
- Man: IF THERE'S
ANYTHING YOU WANT,

2
00:00:13,416 --> 00:00:15,291
ANYTHING AT ALL,
COME TO ME.

3
00:00:15,375 --> 00:00:17,458
I'M YOUR GUARDIAN ANGEL.

4
00:00:17,541 --> 00:00:20,791
- ( theme music playing )

5
00:01:27,541 --> 00:01:29,958
- Ran: IN THE END,

