00:01:30,041 --> 00:01:33,375
YOU WILL DESTROY EVERYTHING.

7
00:01:33,458 --> 00:01:36,458
YOU WILL HURT MANY PEOPLE.

8
00:01:38,291 --> 00:01:41,000
YOU WILL BE ALL ALONE

9
00:01:41,083 --> 00:01:42,791
IN THE END.

10
00:01:48,875 --> 00:01:50,166
- Onishi: I NEVER WOULD HAVE
THOUGHT THAT HE PERSONALLY


11
00:01:50,250 --> 00:01:51,875
KNEW THE SEER.


12
00:01:51,958 --> 00:01:54,750
PERHAPS, THE EXPERIENCE
WILL BE GOOD FOR HIM.


13
00:01:54,833 --> 00:01:57,083
AFTER ALL, RUSHING OFF
TOWARDS ONE'S DOOM

14
00:01:57,166 --> 00:01:59,500
IS THE EASIEST THING
TO DO.

15
00:01:59,583 --> 00:02:01,250
- HE DOESN'T APPEAR TO HAVE
CHANGED TO ME.

16
00:02:06,583 --> 00:02:08,500
- NOBODY GOES UNSCATHED

17
00:02:08,583 --> 00:02:11,333
WHEN THEY'RE TOLD THEIR FUTURE.

18
00:02:13,416 --> 00:02:15,833
I NEED A LITTLE REST.

19
00:02:27,583 --> 00:02:29,666
- Doc: I'VE BEEN SENDING YOU
REPORTS AS WE AGREED.

20
00:02:29,750 --> 00:02:32,291
NOW HOW ABOUT YOU KEEPING
YOUR WORD IN RETURN.

21
00:02:32,375 --> 00:02:35,541
I WON'T DO ANYTHING
LIKE THIS!

22
00:02:52,166 --> 00:02:53,583
- GIMME A GOOD ONE.

23
00:02:53,666 --> 00:02:55,000
I'VE BEEN WORKING
TOO HARD THESE DAYS.

24
00:02:55,083 --> 00:02:57,958
AND IT'S BEEN TAKING
A REAL TOLL ON MY BODY.

25
00:03:16,333 --> 00:03:17,666
- ( gasps )

26
00:03:22,875 --> 00:03:23,958
- ( gunshot )

27
00:04:23,333 --> 00:04:25,541
- Doc: WHAT DO YOU DO
WITH THIS JUNK?

28
00:04:25,625 --> 00:04:29,416
- Man: WELL, I DON'T KNOW.
BUT THERE ARE BUYERS.

29
00:04:29,500 --> 00:04:31,375
- WHO?

30
00:04:53,000 --> 00:04:55,458
THE CLASS?

31
00:05:08,625 --> 00:05:11,916
WHY DO THEY NEED THIS JUNK?

32
00:05:51,583 --> 00:05:55,083
SOMEBODY TOLD ME THAT YOU MIGHT
HAVE SOME RAFFIA HERE.

33
00:05:55,166 --> 00:05:59,083
- WHAT THE HELL IS THAT,
HUH?

34
00:06:01,416 --> 00:06:02,875
- HOW MUCH?

35
00:06:02,958 --> 00:06:04,333
- ( laughs )

36
00:06:12,250 --> 00:06:14,625
- ( gasps )
- I REALLY DON'T HAVE ANY.

37
00:06:14,708 --> 00:06:18,791
