THESE DAYS.

40
00:06:26,166 --> 00:06:28,583
- ( whimpers )

41
00:06:28,666 --> 00:06:29,833
LET GO OF ME.

42
00:06:40,666 --> 00:06:44,708
- COME AGAIN. ( laughs )

43
